TopicTitle: Missing parts after mod update - how to find conflicting mod

Articles.Content:
After updating several mods through CKAN, i am now missing several parts from the RLA Stockalike mod in the VAB (those beautiful micro RCS thrusters). These parts are however still working on active vessels. If i want to launch a saved vessel containing these parts the game indicates the parts are experimental. I checked the science building and they are unlocked.

Can somebody give some hints on how to hunt for the conflicting mod? I'm not sure where to start looking.

 

Thanks!
Your best bet is to probably go ask on the CKAN support thread, since it seems to have started with CKAN...
